Want to learn more about SOLIDWORKS sponsorship, SOLIDWORKS cloud apps and more.
Register now for this upcoming event.

Thursday October 27, 2022
5:00PM EST

Complete Design Freedom is Here! Take your FIRST project to the next level with a new browser-based, 3D design and lifecycle management solution.
The SOLIDWORKS Cloud offer combines the proven design and collaboration tools that allow you and your team members to work together from anywhere, on any device, using a web browser.
In this webinar, We’ll show you how to master your FIRST project with the SOLIDWORKS Cloud Apps powered by the 3DEXPERIENCE Platform

| — | — | — | — |

|>>|Apply to request your license for Cloud Apps.|
|>>|Access to 3DEXPERIENCE Platform and use the Cloud App Tools for CAD Design, Data Management and project coordination.|
|>>|Access to the Student Committee for Support.||

Register here
